White Paper   
Shoot Game

Shoot Game, have the bullet limit. then have the motivition to Kill more Enemy for Bullet.  
Shoot Game, have the Armor. Then have the motivition to Kill more Enemy for Stronger Gun. 
Shoot Game, can assemble new parts for the Gun. Then have the motivation to collect rubbish.  

Logic as this, Get Low Gun, Improve by rubbish Mods. Shoot Mid Gun Enemy. Get Mid Gun, Improve by rubbish Mods, Shoot High Gun Enemy.   

Have a fate to Kill a big boss.
Have a pressue to alive.    


